# SponJIT Measurement Harness — Planned

**Status:** design placeholder. No maintained executable SponJIT runtime exists yet.

The benchmark goal is to measure the future native-stencil / online-fusion pipeline, not the retired C-function path.

## Future measurement target

```text
StencilBank
  -> online fusion planner
  -> FusionPlan
  -> copy/link/patch materializer
  -> LinkedImage execution
```

## What to measure

Runtime measurements:

- active image vs floor entry count;
- fusion planning latency;
- copy/link/patch materialization latency;
- linked image execution time;
- guard/residual/boundary exit rates;
- projection stub cost;
- demotion/replanning frequency;
- image lifetime;
- generated image byte size.

Foundry/offline measurements:

- atom coverage under arity <= 4 and ~32 fact combos;
- rejected atom reasons;
- endpoint/projection contract coverage;
- seam opportunities visible to Tier 2;
- fact-combo usefulness and dedupe rate.

## Non-goals

This bench directory does not currently provide:

- a PUC runtime integration;
- a generated executable stencil bank;
- a native materializer;
- artifact injection hooks;
- C-function stencil benchmarks.

Those pieces must be implemented after the planner/native-stencil ABI gates are satisfied.

